LICENSE NOT YET FINALISED
=========================

The license for this project is intentionally undecided in v0.1 and MUST be set
before any public release.

Leading candidates:

  - AGPL-3.0-or-later  — strong copyleft; keeps forks (including network/SaaS
    forks) open. On-brand for a cypherpunk privacy tool meant to be run locally
    and audited, and discourages a closed re-hosted "attack-as-a-service" fork.

  - MIT / BSD-3-Clause — maximal adoption and citation; minimal friction for
    other privacy projects to reuse parts.

Until this file is replaced with a real license, the work is "all rights
reserved" by default and should not be redistributed.

(c) Cora Aegis — https://cypherpunkguide.com
